<div class="container">
  <div class="headline"> 
    <h1>About The Prop Shop</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="about_intro">
    <div class="top_spacing row">
      <div class="span2">
        <%= image_tag("osrf_logo_only.png", alt:"OSRF Logo") %>
      </div>
    
      <div class="about_text span9 offset1">
        <p>The Prop Shop is brought to you by the <a href="httlp://osrfoundation.org" target="_blank">Open Source Robotics Foundation </a>(OSRF). The Prop Shop is a place for you to share your 3D models for use in simulation environments like <a href="http://gazebosim.org" target="_blank">Gazebo</a>. Share anything from a complex, high degree of freedom robot, to a model of a building, a tool, or a tree. By providing a database for freely-available 3D models, we hope to advance the state of robotic simulation by decreasing the barrier to entry for simulating a robot in a "realistic" simulation environment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about_columns row">
    <div class="creative_commons span6">
      <div class="cc_row">
        <div class="headline">
          <h1>Creative Commons License 3.0</h1>
        </div>

        <p> All models on this website are available to anyone for free under the <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/us/" target="_blank">Creative Commons 3.0 license</a>. If appropriate attribution is made, you may share and adapt the models and/or make commercial use of the work. You can find more information <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/us/" target="_blank">here</a>.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contributing span6">
    	<div class="contributing_row">
        <div class="headline">
          <h1>Contributing Models</h1>
          <p> We encourage you to give back to the community by uploading your own models! We kindly ask that you adhere to the following guidelines:
          </p>
          <ul class="guidelines">
            <li> Login to The Prop Shop. </li>
            <li> Visit the Upload page to submit a new model. </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr style="border: 1px solid #E6E6E6;">

  <div class"about_questions span12">
    <p><strong>Questions?</strong> Visit <a href="http://answers.gazebosim.org">answers.gazebosim.org</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
